<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Coding assistance</b></p><p>If you want to process data from a <span class="code_emphasis">Collection</span> using a <span class="code_emphasis">Stream</span>, start typing the <span class="code_emphasis">Stream</span> method right on a <span class="code_emphasis">Collection</span> instance. IntelliJ IDEA will get the <span class="code_emphasis">Stream</span> instance for you.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/tips_completion_stream.png" alt="Completing Streams" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>